{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/web/ts/tsconfig/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"升高's Blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"01e3cb39-a4f4-566e-89ab-950b7c501aa8","excerpt":"tsconfig.json 配置 1 baseUrl baseUrl 可以使用相对路径去解析模块，值为一个根路径字符串。 如果设置 “baseUrl”: “./“，则 ts 会把与 tsconfig.json 一级的目录设置为根目录。 使用 baseUrl…","html":"<h1>tsconfig.json 配置</h1>\n<h2>1 baseUrl</h2>\n<p>baseUrl 可以使用相对路径去解析模块，值为一个根路径字符串。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"log\"><pre class=\"language-log\"><code class=\"language-log\">baseUrl\n├── <span class=\"token domain constant\">ex.ts</span>\n├── hello\n│   └── <span class=\"token domain constant\">world.ts</span>\n└── tsconfig<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>json</code></pre></div>\n<p>如果设置 “baseUrl”: “./“，则 ts 会把与 tsconfig.json 一级的目录设置为根目录。</p>\n<p>使用 baseUrl 可以避免使用 ”../../” 或者 “./” 等绝对路径引入模块所带来的不方便。</p>\n<h2>2 paths</h2>\n<p>paths 属性可以对导入的路径设置别名，下面是一个例子,从 node_modules 中加载 jquery.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"compilerOptions\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"baseUrl\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\".\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// This must be specified if \"paths\" is.</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"paths\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"jquery\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"node_modules/jquery/dist/jquery\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// This mapping is relative to \"baseUrl\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>需要注意的是 ts 对模块的寻找是相对于 baseUrl 根路径，如果把上面例子中的 baseUrl 设置为 “./src”, 相应的 jquery 应该设置为 “../node_modules/jquery/dist/jquery”</p>\n<p>路径，可以设置为数组的形式，对于下面的例子。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"log\"><pre class=\"language-log\"><code class=\"language-log\">projectRoot\n├── folder1\n│   ├── <span class=\"token domain constant\">file1.ts</span> <span class=\"token operator\">(</span>imports <span class=\"token string\">'folder1/file2'</span> and <span class=\"token string\">'folder2/file3'</span><span class=\"token operator\">)</span>\n│   └── <span class=\"token domain constant\">file2.ts</span>\n├── generated\n│   ├── folder1\n│   └── folder2\n│       └── <span class=\"token domain constant\">file3.ts</span>\n└── tsconfig<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>json</code></pre></div>\n<p>它相应的 tsconfig.json 可能会是这样</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"compilerOptions\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"baseUrl\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\".\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"paths\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"*\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"*\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"generated/*\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ol>\n<li>通配符 ”*” 意味着模块名字不会发生变化，ts 相应的模块查找关系为 moduleName => baseUrl/moduleName。</li>\n<li>“generated/*” 意味着模块的名字有一个附加前缀 “generated”，所以查找关系为 moduleName => baseUrl/generated/moduleName</li>\n</ol>","frontmatter":{"title":"","date":null,"description":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/web/ts/issue/"},"frontmatter":{"title":""}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/web/vue3/communication/"},"frontmatter":{"title":""}}},"pageContext":{"id":"01e3cb39-a4f4-566e-89ab-950b7c501aa8","previousPostId":"e740d925-7f64-52d6-a9b0-7efdd324603a","nextPostId":"11971fe7-db47-52ff-a84f-1dd35cea19ac"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3257411868"]}